                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290115-149-off785 t18290115-149-cd786"></join>, part of two pairs of trousers, value 10s.; 1 waistcoat, value 5s.; 5 handkerchiefs, value 10s.; 3 night-caps, value 1s 6d.; 3 pairs of stockings, value 1s.; 3 knives, value 1s.; 1 frock, value 6d.; 3 boxes, value 20s.; 1 snuff-box, value 2d.; 3 shirts, value 6s.; 1 steel, value 6d., and 1 apron, value 6d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18290115-149-victim1162" type="victimName">
                  William 
                  Bright
               <interp inst="t18290115-149-victim1162" type="surname" value="Bright"></interp>
